## Example Usage

{{< chooser language "typescript,python,go,csharp" / >}}
### Basic
{{% example csharp %}}
```csharp
using Pulumi;
using Docker = Pulumi.Docker;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {
        // Creates a secret
        var fooSecret = new Docker.Secret("fooSecret", new Docker.SecretArgs
        {
            Data = "ewogICJzZXJsaasIfQo=",
        });
    }

}
```
